        <title>How to create a preview thumbnail for a ULR in Apple Notes on iOS and MacOS</title>
        <link>https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/</link>
        <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/thumbnail-generated.jpeg" alt="Featured image of post How to create a preview thumbnail for a ULR in Apple Notes on iOS and MacOS" /&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apple Notes creates beautiful thumbnails for URLs, when you share a URL to the note. Unfortunately, there is no straightforward way to create a thumbnail on demand while you are writing the note, e.g. I&amp;rsquo;d expect smth like long tap ‚Üí create thumbnail or smth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maybe someday we will have an easier way, but for now there is a workaround. It works for both &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/#how-to-create-a-thumbnail-preview-for-a-url-from-within-the-apple-notes-on-ios-iphoneipad&#34; &gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/#how-to-create-a-thumbnail-preview-for-a-url-from-within-the-apple-notes-on-macos-macbook&#34; &gt;MacOS&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;how-to-create-a-thumbnail-preview-for-a-url-from-within-the-apple-notes-on-ios-iphoneipad&#34;&gt;How to create a thumbnail preview for a URL from within the Apple Notes on iOS (iPhone/iPad)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The trick is to &lt;strong&gt;simulate drag-and-drop&lt;/strong&gt; while inside of the app.&lt;br&gt;
In other words, we need force the green  &lt;code&gt;+&lt;/code&gt;  sign to appear.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;method-1-easy&#34;&gt;Method 1, easy&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This method was proposed by &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/shorts/8T088LlOxko&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;@soundsgoodtome on YouTube&lt;/a&gt; in comments under the first video I have published on this topic with (&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/#method-2-original&#34; &gt;Method 2&lt;/a&gt;). Since then I am only using Method 1.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/undo-redo-1.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;1179&#34;
	height=&#34;2556&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/undo-redo-1_hu0039bba89a66a7de1164b428f30945a3_147823_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 480w, https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/undo-redo-1_hu0039bba89a66a7de1164b428f30945a3_147823_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;eager&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;holding URL, drag-and-drop mode off&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;46&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;110px&#34;
	
&gt;
 &lt;img src=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/undo-redo-2.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;1179&#34;
	height=&#34;2556&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/undo-redo-2_huf7a706ae1953d2595b15078d9f8ecc42_172068_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 480w, https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/undo-redo-2_huf7a706ae1953d2595b15078d9f8ecc42_172068_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;eager&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;drag-and-drop mode activated after tapping on UNDO&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;46&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;110px&#34;
	
&gt;
 &lt;img src=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/undo-redo-3.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;1179&#34;
	height=&#34;2556&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/undo-redo-3_hu41e3049ffa0150dbf18984003c49350d_188600_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 480w, https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/undo-redo-3_hu41e3049ffa0150dbf18984003c49350d_188600_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;eager&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;pasted thumbnail preview&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;46&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;110px&#34;
	
&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;create/open a note&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;paste/type textual URL to the note&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;tap and hold on the URL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;tap with another finger on the UNDO button&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;green plus should appear near the plate with the URL as drag-and-drop mode activates at that moment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;5&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;tap REDO to preserve the state of the note after pressing UNDO&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;remove finger from the screen to paste the thumbnail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;video-wrapper&#34;&gt;
    &lt;iframe loading=&#34;lazy&#34; 
            src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/VJIVwmABwLw&#34; 
            allowfullscreen 
            title=&#34;YouTube Video&#34;
    &gt;
    &lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&#34;method-2-original&#34;&gt;Method 2, original&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This method is somewhat tricky, hence not recommended.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;create/open a note&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;paste/type textual URL to the note&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;dismiss keyboard (swipe down outside of the keyboard)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;tap and hold on the URL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;move it out of the way so that you can see the body of the note&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;tap with another finger on the body of the note (goal is to call the keyboard again)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;at that point, green plus should appear near the plate with the URL you should still be holding with your finger&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;8&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;point with the cursor where you would like to place the thumbnail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;remove finger from the screen to paste the thumbnail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/apple-note-2.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;1179&#34;
	height=&#34;2556&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/apple-note-2_hu7ef010e7ebe8b311b72349d6fb290120_142857_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 480w, https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/apple-note-2_hu7ef010e7ebe8b311b72349d6fb290120_142857_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;eager&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;holding URL plate without on-screen keyboard&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;46&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;110px&#34;
	
&gt;
 &lt;img src=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/apple-note-3.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;1179&#34;
	height=&#34;2556&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/apple-note-3_hu7ef010e7ebe8b311b72349d6fb290120_227531_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 480w, https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/apple-note-3_hu7ef010e7ebe8b311b72349d6fb290120_227531_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;eager&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;holding URL plate with on-screen keyboard - green &amp;#43; is visible&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;46&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;110px&#34;
	
&gt;
 &lt;img src=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/apple-note-4.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;1179&#34;
	height=&#34;2556&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/apple-note-4_hu7ef010e7ebe8b311b72349d6fb290120_183124_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 480w, https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/apple-note-4_hu7ef010e7ebe8b311b72349d6fb290120_183124_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;eager&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;thumbnail inserted&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;46&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;110px&#34;
	
&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For some really weird reason, sometimes this plus appears later, so occasionally the process needs to be repeated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;video-wrapper&#34;&gt;
    &lt;iframe loading=&#34;lazy&#34; 
            src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/8T088LlOxko&#34; 
            allowfullscreen 
            title=&#34;YouTube Video&#34;
    &gt;
    &lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;how-to-create-a-thumbnail-preview-for-a-url-from-within-the-apple-notes-on-macos-macbook&#34;&gt;How to create a thumbnail preview for a URL from within the Apple Notes on MacOS (Macbook)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can do the same on MacOS, but the process is a bit different and even more weird. The principle remains the same - we need to drag-and-drop the URL to the body of the note.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must have a trackpad for this to work, as you will need forcetouch to open the quick preview of the URL.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;create/open a note&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;paste/type textual URL to the note&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;use trackpad to click and hold on the URL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;the preview will open (you can release the trackpad)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;click and drag the URL from the preview; you need to select URL which will lead to the page you want to create a thumbnail for.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;drag the URL-plate to the body of the note&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;release the trackpad to paste the thumbnail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;repeat if needed, as you can drop as many thumbnails as you want from this preview (it won&amp;rsquo;t close until you click outside of it)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/macos-1.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;824&#34;
	height=&#34;1020&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/macos-1_hu891c2f83036833b54f1a3b5ac4cc3ee0_38144_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/macos-1_hu891c2f83036833b54f1a3b5ac4cc3ee0_38144_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;eager&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;pick URL from the page you want to create thumbnail for&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;80&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;193px&#34;
	
&gt;
 &lt;img src=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/macos-2.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;824&#34;
	height=&#34;1020&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/macos-2_hua22f3e3f9cccb2fe3c1ac3f886d4eb57_39759_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://1ar.io/p/thumbnail-apple-notes/macos-2_hua22f3e3f9cccb2fe3c1ac3f886d4eb57_39759_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;eager&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;drop it off to the note&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;80&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;193px&#34;
	
&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here is a video to demonstrate the process on macos:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;video-wrapper&#34;&gt;
    &lt;iframe loading=&#34;lazy&#34; 
            src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/0AETyMolDCw&#34; 
            allowfullscreen 
            title=&#34;YouTube Video&#34;
    &gt;
    &lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I hope it helps and would be happy if you could let me know if you can reproduce this. Feel free drop a comment here, &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://x.com/pa1ar/status/1744852069385994705?s=20&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;tag/DM me on ùïè&lt;/a&gt; or drop a comment on &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/@pa1ar&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;YouTube&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.tiktok.com/@1ar.io/video/7322218545662807329?is_from_webapp=1&amp;amp;sender_device=pc&amp;amp;web_id=7319913510544295457&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;TikTok&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
